        "text_eJ4mCm": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The Footwear Development Package is our most comprehensive package to create better fitting and functioning footwear utilizing complete, accurate 3D foot data. The package includes full access to Foot.com, plus special software features including advanced measurement tools and analysis programs.</p><h2>Package Includes:</h2><ul><li>Albert Pro Scanner</li><li>Special Software with Advanced Features for Development</li></ul><p><strong>Foot.com Data</strong> – Access to comprehensive global 3D foot data and pressure data underfoot, remote access, and the ability to 3D print foot models for fit testing.</p><p><strong>Wear Tester</strong> – AI-driven comparison and data analysis tool to identify the most accurate physical wear tester profiles for your business.</p><p><strong>“Lasso” Tool</strong> – 3D measurement tool for calculating infinite measurements of the foot on individual scans.</p>",
            "text_font": "body",
            "text_size": "subtext-md",
            "text_max_size": 32,
            "text_line_height": 1.6,
