    "image_with_text_Cq3wRG": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_ALfqUD": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>Wear Tester Software</h3><h6><strong>Identify Accurate Wear Testers in a Snap!</strong></h6><p>Footwear developers rely heavily on the feedback of wear testers. But, how do you really know if the wear tester’s feet represent an ideal sample for the population?<br/><br/>The Aetrex Wear Tester Software is designed to help footwear teams learn how to identify the most accurate physical wear tester profiles based on their 3D foot characteristics.<br/><br/>The program works by using AI to compare comprehensive 3D foot scans of a company’s wear tester candidates to millions of foot profiles collected from the general population around the world. Potential wear tester profiles are then assigned a score for their comparison accuracy of the desired sample size per region. Footwear brands can use the scores to identify the most accurate wear testers for their brand, ensuring the best fit for their shoes.<br/><br/></p>",
            "text_font": "body",
            "text_size": "subtext-sm",
            "text_max_size": 32,
            "text_line_height": 1.6,
            "text_letter_spacing": 0,
